{"tid":193033,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"屎忽痕留咗陣頭髮，依家又屎忽痕想剪返短頭髮....","createTime":"2017-04-09T04:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T02:56:11.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abff461d17c4160afcd5b265f6b8c78317a9cace","tid":193033,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗唔到留咩頭<br />\n身邊個個都叫我剪返短髮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗緊剪唔剪好"},{"pid":"457a2a4ebbf1d9b7e923e46566172020f927e68b","tid":193033,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"留到幾長先？"},{"pid":"f3631d37c6a1412e81ff1cf73a435aab3083a8d4","tid":193033,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留到幾長先？</blockquote><br />\n唔長，兩邊貼耳<br />\n後面就嚟cover成條頸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身剪開剷青個啲<br />\n所以咁都叫留咗陣..."},{"pid":"050ed1e9306448a082dc9da9cc6ded29470b7554","tid":193033,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"呢排開始熱啦 剷啦"},{"pid":"5d0425a929bd5663048fa9826260d1f5dfdc3ecb","tid":193033,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"半邊頭留長 半邊剷短lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b87c88051c4450cbcbede0646b8f1506ecce3dd","tid":193033,"uid":15287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"十個長髮九個身邊都有人叫佢剪返短<br />\n啲人叫你剪短原因多數唔係因為你留長唔好睇<br />\n而係香港人接受唔到 除非真係好唔夾你個樣<br />\n你自己想唔想長髮先 想嘅話咪留 唔長唔短未搞好 係人都有柒頭期<br />\n真係唔洗理人意見 你留得型/佢哋睇慣咗自然收聲<br />\n當你留到真係點整都唔好睇咪剪返短<br />\n但依家未試又剪短 遲下屎忽痕留返又晒時間 留到一半又剪 loop<br />\n<br />\n熱唔熱就睇你本身係咪大汗 怕唔怕<br />\n不過對我嚟講都係籍口 我又長髮又怕熱又返辛苦工<br />\n<br />\n老實講我唔覺得自己留得好睇 <br />\n但on9講句長髮係一種態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真男人留長髮唔應該猶豫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda8923b98873b5b6ef34f39b10c58e4ff923961","tid":193033,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"如果唔係非主流髮型果D長髮, 係香港係唔會有奇怪目光的, 放心"},{"pid":"c183ed64e85ed8df2103b50efc5bf8f8aa80d309","tid":193033,"uid":55656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:40:36.000Z","msg":"留埋佢啦<br />\n我都留緊"},{"pid":"54cb38b2b9bc6d372841fde16ac7d8eb3ee5db6f","tid":193033,"uid":10687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:43:46.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"bcf68f31ee8f22803c2eff793be92dcced66de11","tid":193033,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"我都 剪 左短<br />\n費事 焗成額汗 好辛苦"},{"pid":"fd9bc0cdbad7e7fac9c0b4fe409980fbe4f6f3f7","tid":193033,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:38:39.000Z","msg":"我長到落頸 現家熱到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bec6f66cfa22812c2b3071beac98016fb46748","tid":193033,"uid":63345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"又係你，扭扭擰擰成個女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}